data.description:
Welcome to your new home in the heart of Eagle! This beautiful 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhouse is available for rent, and it's ready for you to move in and make it your own. With its spacious and open floor plan, this townhouse is perfect for entertaining friends and family. The living room features a spacious area and plenty of natural light, making it the perfect spot to relax and unwind. 

The kitchen comes fully equipped with appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of cabinets. The master suite in this townhouse is a spacious and cozy room. Located on the second floor, it offers a peaceful and private oasis from the rest of the home. The bedroom itself is generously sized and features large window overlooking the common grounds out back. And with its designer tile and neutral color palette, the space feels warm and inviting. 

This townhouse also boasts a private patio and short access to a public back yard, perfect for enjoying Idaho's beautiful weather and outdoor activities. Located in the heart of Eagle community, this townhouse is close to great schools, parks, restaurants, and shopping. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property your new home!

Looking for a one year lease. A washer/dryer and refrigerator is included in rent as well as owner will pay for water, sewer, trash, landscaping, and HOA fees. Tenant will just need to cover electric and internet if they desire. We are open to allowing dogs. Tenant must have renters insurance. Qualification are 550+ credit score, 2.5x monthly income to rent ratio and a clean background. Accepting pets on a per scenario basis.
